found nearly naked, badly beaten and smeared with blood.
   Smith, 23, who has been in and out of mental hospitals for
years, has admitted he killed the woman but contends he was insane
and not responsible for the act.
   Rosenthal, then chief of detectives, arrested Smith in the
cafeteria of a men's shelter, where Smith sometimes lived.
